# Antigravity-native variant of .aiexclude (.gitignore syntax). Kept alongside
# .aiexclude because which file a given Antigravity build reads is version-dependent;
# both are zero-cost and an unrecognized one is simply ignored.
# Secret-hiding only — not a hard security boundary.
.env
.env.*
.envrc
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
secrets/
